title: Kudrat Ka Kanoon
subTitle: When the good doctor Vijay is falsely accused and imprisoned, his wife and daughter, desperately seeking justice, are terrorised and slandered by the harsh eyes of the society.

title: Trimurti
subTitle: A wrongfully convicted policewoman expects her three children to settle scores with her enemy. But when the long-awaited moment arrives, luck does not seem to be on her side.

title: Police Aur Mujrim
subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

subTitle: A businessman disowns his spoiled son, Aditya, after he marries a girl from a rival family. Upon discovering his father's lung cancer, Aditya resolves to change for the better.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Ram Teri Ganga Maili
subTitle: When Ganga's husband abandons her, she embarks on a journey to Calcutta to find him and ensure her son has a better future. But she is cheated and forced to work in a brothel.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Nadiya Ke Paar
subTitle: Chandan, a farmer's nephew, is in love with Gunja, his sister-in-law's sibling. However, when her sister dies in an accident, Gunja is expected to marry Chandan's brother.

title: The Bhootnii
subTitle: After a heartbreak, Shantanu unknowingly summons a spirit named Mohabbat, whose obsessive presence begins to disrupt the peace of the entire college campus.

subTitle: Bankhelal, who started his career by selling milk, soon becomes a famous ruthless criminal. However, the only person he fears is Inspector Vishal as he has sworn to apprehend him.

title: Sansar
subTitle: A family's harmony is disrupted by a disagreement between parents and their children. Later, the daughter-in-law intervenes, aiming to reunite the family.

title: Aadmi
subTitle: Vijay, a factory supervisor, is falsely accused and arrested for killing his family. Just when he is at his lowest point, an inspector offers to help him in return for capturing the son of a gangster.

title: Avtaar
subTitle: Avtaar leads a happy life with his wife, Radha, and his sons, Chander and Ramesh. However, consumed by their greed and ambitions, Avtaar's sons betray him but he soon reaches new heights of success.

title: Insaaf Kaun Karega
subTitle: Jageera abandons his wife and son Vikram to join a life of crime. Years later, when Vikram, now a police officer, sets out to put an end to Jageera's activities, he swears to kill him.

title: Mr. India
subTitle: Hoping to make the world a better place for orphaned children, a compassionate street musician takes on a power-hungry crime boss with the help of a cloaking device.

title: Jodidar
subTitle: Ganesh, an elephant, watches his master being killed by three poachers. After many years, Ganesh can identify the killers while being in the service of a new master, Munna.

title: Mr. Bond
subTitle: Mr Bond is a detective known for solving the toughest of crime mysteries. But the arrival of Dragon, a gangster involved in child-trafficking, seems to be a real challenge for the crime-solver.

subTitle: A young reporter, Prashant Verma, tired of injustice, bears witness to a murder case and wages war against Tau. But in the process, his life and family members get threatened.

subTitle: A young man faces relationship trials when the parents of the woman he loves decide to get her married off to another suitor.

title: Daanveer

title: Khal Nayak
subTitle: Inspector Ram succeeds in nabbing notorious criminal Ballu. When Ballu's escape taints Ram's name, his fianc√©e, Ganga, decides to trap Ballu. But, things get complicated when Ballu starts liking her.

title: Don
subTitle: Don, a wanted criminal, succumbs to his injuries in a police chase. Things take a turn when Vijay, a lookalike of Don, replaces him and tries to trace the details of his illegal activities.

title: Shaktiman
subTitle: When Vicky and Amar get switched at birth, one grows up to be a police officer and the other a murderer. Things take a turn when their parents learn the truth.
